                    <h2 id="app-title-line2" class="text-[10px] min-[375px]:text-[11.5px] sm:text-base md:text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight sm:tracking-wide drop-shadow-md leading-tight whitespace-nowrap mt-[1px]"></h2>
